original_title: Lucha Libre AAA Invading New York
overview: Lucha Libre AAA Invading New York was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) event produced and scripted by the Mexican professional wrestling promotion Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide (AAA or Triple A), in partnership with Impact Wrestling. The event took place on September 15, 2019, at Madison Square Garden's Hulu Theater in New York City, New York. The event aired live on traditional PPV outlets and FITE TV in the US.
tagline: Mexico's premier lucha libre wrestlers are coming to New York
title: Lucha Libre AAA Invading New York
